Task #5: Mistral-nemo LLM + Account/Profile Page

## Backend changes
- chat_service.py: OLLAMA_MODEL changed to "mistral-nemo"; ollama_chat() uses Ollama
  /api/chat endpoint with messages array for multi-turn memory; conversation_history param
  (list of {role,content} dicts) prepended to messages; _build_system_message() helper;
  get_workout_tip() switched to /api/chat; ensure_model_available() updated with 600s timeout.
- chatbot.py: Added conversationHistory: Optional[List[Dict]] to ChatRequest; forwarded
  to ollama_chat().

## Ollama workflow
- Updated .replit Ollama LLM workflow to: ollama pull mistral-nemo 2>/dev/null || true; ollama serve

## Frontend API + multi-turn chat
- /api/chat/route.js: Accepts and forwards conversationHistory to backend.
- AICoach.js: messagesRef tracks latest messages; send() captures history snapshot and
  sends as conversationHistory.
- page.js FloatingChatbot: Same messagesRef pattern; sends conversationHistory.

## Account screen (new, frontend/screens/Account.js)
- 128px circular avatar (upload photo as base64 → fitai_avatar localStorage, OR choose
  from 12 preset emoji avatars → fitai_avatar_emoji).
- Editable fields: Name, Age, Weight (kg), Height (cm), Fitness Goal (dropdown with 5
  options), Fitness Level (dropdown with 3 options).
- Save button writes to fitai_user localStorage.
- Animated floating bottom toast notification (green, 2.5s) on save.
- Back button via onBack prop; onProfileUpdated callback for parent state refresh.

## Settings cleanup (frontend/screens/Settings.js)
- Large blue profile card removed.
- Compact "Account & Profile" row at top: shows avatar thumbnail + label "ACCOUNT & PROFILE" 
  + display name + chevron.
- onNavigate('account') prop triggers navigation to Account screen.
- Logout moved to dedicated bottom section.

## Navigation wiring (frontend/app/page.js)
- Account imported + added to SCREEN_MAP (not in NAV_IDS).
- Header avatar navigates to Account (not logout); shows photo/emoji/initials.
- prevActive tracked to enable Back navigation; guards added to avoid overwriting prevActive
  when already on Account.
- refreshProfile callback: reads localStorage and increments profileVersion on save so
  header avatar/initials update immediately without requiring navigation.
- Updated initials computation to support name field (in addition to first_name/last_name).

## CSS fix
- globals.css: Added --warning dark mode variable (was missing in .dark block).
